      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. but the clause i'm looking at says i have to indemnify them against \"all third-party claims and liabilities.\" that sounds kind of scary... like if someone sues them for something i didn't even do, i'm still on the hook? is that how it works?",
